605
01:29:37,200 --> 01:29:40,100
Anh Akon, khỏe không?

606
01:30:33,300 --> 01:30:34,460
Wick đang ở đây!

607
01:30:34,530 --> 01:30:36,430
Vâng.

608
01:31:25,450 --> 01:31:28,350
